 Hajj: Speak kind words, feed poor in pilgrimage","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 25, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Jabir ibn Abdullah reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe righteous Hajj pilgrimage has no reward but Paradise.\u201d Jabir said, \u201cWhat is its righteousness?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cTo feed the poor and speak kind words.\u201d Source: al-Mu\u2019jam al-Awsat\u0323 8629 Grade:\u00a0Sahih li ghayrihi (authentic due to external\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":9353,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/29\/treat-people-as-you-like-to-be-treated\/","url_meta":{"origin":33136,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Faith: Treat people how you love to be treated","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 29, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu al-Muntafiq reported: I said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, teach me what will save me from the punishment of Allah and admit me into Paradise.\u201d The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWorship Allah and do not associate anything with Him, establish the prescribed prayers, give\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32768,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/07\/12\/islam-vanishes-end-of-time\/","url_meta":{"origin":33136,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Islam: Disappearance of religious knowledge at end of time","author":"